@startuml
' Diagram: F03b - Hang doi audio thuyet minh per-device (Sequence, sub-sequence cua F03)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 2497a96
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/MainPage.xaml.cs: QueuePoiPlayback(), ProcessSpeakQueueAsync(), SpeakPoiAsync(), LogPlaybackAsync(), OnListenClicked()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/ThuyetMinhController.cs: GetByPoi()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/LogController.cs: Post()
' Note: Sequence mo phong tinh huong "user di chuyen qua nhieu POI lien tuc" + "user bam Nghe lai trong khi POI khac dang phat" de cho thay 3 lop chong trung.
' Note: Day la queue per-device. Khi nhieu khach cung vao 1 POI, moi may co _speakQueue rieng; KHONG co server-side queue.
title F03b - Hang doi audio thuyet minh per-device

actor Guest
participant CheckGeofence
participant QueuePoiPlayback
participant "_speakQueue\n_queuedSpeakPoiIds\n(lock _speakQueueGate)" as Q
participant ProcessSpeakQueueAsync as Proc
participant "SpeakPoiAsync\n(qua _speakLock\nsemaphore)" as Speak
participant "ThuyetMinhController" as ThuyetMinh
participant "LogController" as LogC
participant "TextToSpeech" as TTS
database DB

== Tinh huong 1: Vao POI A lan dau ==

CheckGeofence -> QueuePoiPlayback: QueuePoiPlayback(A)
QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: lock + check
Q --> QueuePoiPlayback: _playingPoi=null, queue rong\n_queuedSpeakPoiIds khong co A
QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: enqueue(A) + add A vao set\n_isProcessingSpeakQueue = true
QueuePoiPlayback -> Proc: start ProcessSpeakQueueAsync()\n(tren MainThread)

Proc -> Q: lock + dequeue
Q --> Proc: A (queue rong sau do)
Proc -> Speak: await SpeakPoiAsync(A)
Speak -> Speak: await _speakLock.WaitAsync()
Speak -> ThuyetMinh: GET /api/thuyet-minh/{A.Id}?lang=vi
ThuyetMinh -> DB: load BanDich(vi)
DB --> ThuyetMinh: NoiDung
ThuyetMinh --> Speak: ThuyetMinhResponse
Speak -> Speak: _playingPoi = A\nShowNowPlaying(A)
Speak -> TTS: SpeakAsync(content, locale)
TTS --> Speak: done
Speak -> LogC: POST /api/log (poiId=A, Nguon=GPS)
LogC -> DB: insert LichSuPhat
Speak -> Speak: _playingPoi = null\nHideNowPlaying()\n_speakLock.Release()

Proc -> Q: lock + check (rong)
Q --> Proc: empty
Proc -> Proc: _isProcessingSpeakQueue = false\nreturn

== Tinh huong 2: Dang phat A, user di sang POI B (khong cooldown) ==

CheckGeofence -> QueuePoiPlayback: QueuePoiPlayback(B)
QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: lock + check
Q --> QueuePoiPlayback: _playingPoi = A (dang phat)\nA != B, B chua co trong set
QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: enqueue(B) + add B vao set
note right of Q
  Khong cancel A — A van phat
  het roi moi den B (FIFO).
  Day la y do thiet ke: user
  duoc nghe het thuyet minh.
end note
QueuePoiPlayback -> QueuePoiPlayback: _isProcessingSpeakQueue=true (da chay)\n-> KHONG start processor moi
QueuePoiPlayback --> CheckGeofence: return

... A van dang TTS ...

Speak -> Speak: A xong, _speakLock.Release()
Proc -> Q: lock + dequeue tiep
Q --> Proc: B
Proc -> Speak: await SpeakPoiAsync(B)
note right of Speak
  Cung dung _speakLock semaphore -
  vi A da release nen B WaitAsync
  duoc cap, KHONG chong cheo TTS.
end note
Speak -> ThuyetMinh: GET /api/thuyet-minh/{B.Id}
Speak -> TTS: SpeakAsync(content B)
TTS --> Speak: done
Speak -> LogC: POST /api/log (poiId=B)

== Tinh huong 3: Re-enqueue POI A (chong trung) ==

CheckGeofence -> QueuePoiPlayback: QueuePoiPlayback(A)\n(GPS jitter, dwell trigger lai)
QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: lock + check
alt A dang phat (_playingPoi.Id == A.Id)
  Q --> QueuePoiPlayback: HIT lop 1: _playingPoi == A
  QueuePoiPlayback --> CheckGeofence: SKIP (return ngay)
else A da trong queue (_queuedSpeakPoiIds.Contains(A.Id))
  Q --> QueuePoiPlayback: HIT lop 2: A da queued
  QueuePoiPlayback --> CheckGeofence: SKIP (return ngay)
else A khong dang phat va khong trong queue
  note right of QueuePoiPlayback
    Vi du: user roi A > 10 phut, vao lai.
    Cooldown da het, va A da phat xong
    nen khong con trong _playingPoi/_queuedSpeakPoiIds.
    -> Chap nhan enqueue lai.
  end note
  Q --> QueuePoiPlayback: chua co
  QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: enqueue(A)
end

== Tinh huong 4: User bam "Nghe lai" tu MainPage ==

Guest -> CheckGeofence: bam BtnListen (OnListenClicked)
CheckGeofence -> QueuePoiPlayback: QueuePoiPlayback(_currentPoi)
QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: lock + check
alt _currentPoi dang phat
  Q --> QueuePoiPlayback: SKIP (lop 1)
else _currentPoi da trong queue
  Q --> QueuePoiPlayback: SKIP (lop 2)
else hop le
  QueuePoiPlayback -> Q: enqueue\n(qua _speakLock semaphore khi den luot)
end
@enduml
